<p><a name="Work_on_Broadway" id="Work_on_Broadway"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Paul_Simon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Work on Broadway">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Work on Broadway</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><i>Rock 'N Roll! The First 5,000 Years</i> (1982) - <a href="/wiki/Revue" title="Revue">revue</a> - featured <a href="/wiki/Songwriter" title="Songwriter">songwriter</a> for <a href="/wiki/Mrs._Robinson" title="Mrs. Robinson">Mrs. Robinson</a></li>
<li><i>Asinamali!</i> (1987) - play - co-<a href="/wiki/Theatrical_producer" title="Theatrical producer">producer</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Mike_Nichols" title="Mike Nichols">Mike Nichols</a> and <a href="/wiki/Elaine_May" title="Elaine May">Elaine May</a>: Together Again on Broadway</i> (1992) - <a href="/wiki/Concert" title="Concert">concert</a> - performer</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Capeman" title="The Capeman">The Capeman</a></i> (1998) - <a href="/wiki/Composer" title="Composer">composer</a>, co-<a href="/wiki/Lyricist" title="Lyricist">lyricist</a> and <a href="/wiki/Arrangement" title="Arrangement">music arranger</a> - <a href="/wiki/Tony_Award" title="Tony Award">Tony</a> Nomination for <a href="/wiki/Tony_Award_for_Best_Original_Score" title="Tony Award for Best Original Score">Best Original Score</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Graduate" title="The Graduate">The Graduate</a></i> (2002) - play - featured <a href="/wiki/Songwriter" title="Songwriter">songwriter</a></li>
</ul>
